# Ignite-Project
Do you have allergies to certain food products? Are you tired of always having to read the labels and see if any allergens are in that product?
This app is the perfect solution for you! By inputting your allergies, the app allows you to scan any food item using the camera and will bold all of your allergies (if any) in that product.
It will them give you a check mark or X if that product is safe to eat, or not.
